  "title": "Variant Composters",
  "description": "Composters in all wood types",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Composters/BH_VC_Title_5.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.revivalinchrist.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/line-break-png-1.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7688001/184992833-c17504b1-48a2-4633-b19e-9cc7a1e85790.png\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.revivalinchrist.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/line-break-png-1.png\" /></p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Mod compatibility included for :</span></strong></span></h6>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><strong>1.0</strong>&nbsp;- Epic Paladins, Tech Reborn<br /></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><strong>1.0.1</strong> - Simple Mango<br /><strong>1.0.2 -&nbsp;</strong>Traverse<br /><strong>1.0.3</strong> - Terrestria</span></span></span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>1.0.4</strong> - Cinderscapes<br /><strong>1.0.5</strong>&nbsp;- Farmer POI Support<br /><strong>1.0.6</strong>&nbsp;- Colorful Azaleas</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><br /><img src=\"https://www.revivalinchrist.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/line-break-png-1.png\" /></span></span></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">All textures have been compressed (without any negative impact) to keep the mod file size to an absolute minimum.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">All textures are manually created using the the appropriate planks to ensure they look correct.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Fabric load conditions have been used to ensure your console is not full of errors when compatible mods are not installed.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">It has also been used to stop any duplicate composters appearing, for example : if Better Nether is installed the Warped &amp; Crimson crafting tables are disabled.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Un-crafting for all variants back to vanilla has been included in case of any issues.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px;\">Vanilla Composter renamed to Spruce and recoloured slightly to better fit the Spruce wood type.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.revivalinchrist.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/line-break-png-1.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Please also consider downloading my other mods</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Barrels -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-barrels-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-barrels-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Bookshelves -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-bookshelves-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-bookshelves-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Crafting Tables -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-crafting-tables-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-crafting-tables-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Grindstones -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-grindstones-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-grindstones-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Lanterns -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-lanterns-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-lanterns-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Shields -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-tiered-shields-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-tiered-shields-fabric</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Sticks &amp; Stuff -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-sticks-stuff\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-sticks-stuff</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Variant Weapons &amp; Tools -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-weapons-tools-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-weapons-tools-fabric</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><a href=\"https://discord.gg/tmwxB2sceU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/shingekinokyojin/images/4/42/Discord_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"64\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Composters/BH_VC_BisectPromo_5.png\" /></span></p>",
